apps/1927570/extras/Sword.png?t=1665675830\" /> Over 100 items and passive treasures<br><br><br>All these make for tons of different strategies and maps to discover as you go, and even more secrets, Easter eggs and special interactions wait around every corner!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927570/extras/Steam_Separator_x3.png?t=1665675830\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Nagnus Will Remember That.</h2>Buy upgrades? Pff. Where do you think you are, the underworld? <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927570/extras/Rat.png?t=1665675830\" /><br><br>You unlock upgrades by doing specific things inside the game! How about finding the blacksmith\u2019s lost tools to unlock free equipment every run? Or try beating the lord of hell himself for a permanent power boon! There are loads of upgrades that persist from run to run, and they are all beautifully integrated into the gameplay and story!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927570/extras/Steam_Separator_x3.png?t=1665675830\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open To Feedback</h2>You dig it but not quite there yet? Let me know and I'll try my hardest to make the game the best version of itself! You can mail me directly, message me on Steam or even tweet to me!<br><br>The Press Kit is available at the Website Link on Steam.","developers":["Dave Doublee"],"genres":[{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927570/header.jpg?t=1665675830","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256882577,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256882577/movie480.mp4?t=1653757624","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256882577/movie_max.mp4?t=1653757624"},"na